  <brief_title>Effects of Bile Acids and Bile Acid Sequestrants on GLP-1 Secretion After Roux-en-Y Gastric Bypass</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Chenodeoxycholic Acid and Colesevelam on GLP-1 Secretion, During a Meal, After Roux-en-Y Gastric Bypass</official_title>
