  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the effects of bile acid and bile acids sequestrants&#xD;
      on GLP-1 Secretion, during a meal, in patients after Roux-en-Y gastric bypass.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
